rt trails and have our boots cleaned down with a bleach solution.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Radio Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anthony Waddle\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"the brickpit\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"boggy\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"4WD dirt trails\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"our boots\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"a bleach solution\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Protection from the neighbouring modern world makes for ideal conditions to conserve the frog, says Macquarie University biologist Anthony Waddle.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2200975402937342e-20, \"text\": \"Macquarie University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Protection\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"the neighbouring modern world\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"ideal conditions\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the frog\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is great habitat for the frogs to breed in, for tadpoles to grow up in,\\\" Dr Waddle said.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great habitat\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"the frogs\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"tadpoles\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr Waddle\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scattered around the quarry are the weapons used in the battle to save the frogs from the killer chytrid fungus, which has been linked to the extinction of 90 frog species around the world.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the quarry\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"the weapons\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"the battle\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"the frogs\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"the killer chytrid fungus\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the extinction\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"90 frog species\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dozens of small greenhouses dot the landscape, each containing a tower of black-painted masonry bricks.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dozens\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"small greenhouses\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"the landscape\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"a tower\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"black-painted masonry bricks\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a simple solution built from basic things bought from a hardware warehouse.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a simple solution\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"basic things\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"a hardware warehouse\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The greenhouses are known as \\\"frog saunas\\\" because of the way they heat up in sunlight.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The greenhouses\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"frog saunas\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"sunlight\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A green and golden bell frog found by Dr Waddle at the Sydney Olympic Park brickpit.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A green and golden bell frog\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr Waddle\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sydney Olympic Park brickpit\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC Radio Sydney: Declan Bowring) Chytrid is at its most deadly in the winter.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Radio Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chytridiomycota\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chytrid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chytridiomycota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chytridiomycota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Declan Bowring\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"the winter\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Combating the fungus requires a solution that is inviting for the frogs and keeps them warm.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fungus\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"a solution\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"the frogs\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As it happens, standard masonry bricks have \\\"frog-sized\\\" holes in them, as Dr Waddle describes them, and the greenhouses warm them up when in contact with direct sunlight.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"standard masonry bricks\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"frog-sized\\\" holes\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr Waddle\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"the greenhouses\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"direct sunlight\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The materials that make up \\\"frog saunas\\\" can be found at hardware stores.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The materials\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"frog saunas\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"hardware stores\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC Radio Sydney: Declan Bowring) In Dr Waddle's research published in the journalNature, frogs not only were attracted to the saunas but became more resilient to chytrid and were resistant to subsequent infections.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2111, \"end\": 2127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Radio Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Declan Bowring\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr Waddle's research\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"the journalNature\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"frogs\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"the saunas\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"chytrid\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"subsequent infections\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We found that if you can simply keep the frogs a bit warm in winter you can prevent them from dying.\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the frogs\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"winter\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having high humidity and heat is really key to attracting the frogs and also getting rid of their chytrid infections.\\\"\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high humidity\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"the frogs\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"their chytrid infections\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dozens of small greenhouses are scattered around the old brickpit.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dozens\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"small greenhouses\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"the old brickpit\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC Radio Sydney: Declan Bowring) While ABC Radio Sydney was visiting the site with Dr Waddle, he found the first green and yellow bell frog that had naturally made a home inside one of his frog saunas.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2620, \"end\": 2636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Radio Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 2661, \"end\": 2677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Radio Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Declan Bowring\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr Waddle\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"the first green and yellow bell frog\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"a home\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"his frog saunas\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a fitting new chapter in the history of bricks, many of which were made in the same pit the research is taking place in.\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fitting new chapter\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2851}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"bricks\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"the same pit\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"the research\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The brickpit was saved from development before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The brickpit\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"development\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC Radio Sydney: Declan Bowring) It's also a fitting new chapter for the area, which was spared from development before the 2000 Sydney Olympics when the endangered frogs were discovered at the site.\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3013, \"end\": 3029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Radio Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3159, \"title\"