\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"viral fame\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 3398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is pleased by how widely his work has spread, connecting him with fans including a pottery club on the NSW South Coast looking to make frog saunas in their area.\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3507, \"end\": 3522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Coast_(New_South_Wales)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NSW South Coast\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Coast_(New_South_Wales)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Coast_(New_South_Wales)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his work\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3437}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3474}, {\"ngram\": \"a pottery club\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"frog saunas\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"their area\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Waddle hopes the viral moment will help propel his simple solution around the country.\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dr Waddle\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"the viral moment\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3599}, {\"ngram\": \"his simple solution\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC Radio Sydney: Declan Bowring) He is encouraging the public to get involved and has published anonline guide of how to build the saunas.\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3657, \"end\": 3673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Radio Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ng